        "type": "text",
        "name": null,
        "title": null,
        "style": null,
        "decorator": null,
        "content": "<h3>Starting from our smartphones, the increased levels of connections in the world are changing industries at an alarming rate. For many brands interested in taking full advantage of thing commerce, it&#39;s key to find a way to connect their services to the internet.</h3>\n\n<p>Thing commerce creates an improved visibility fulfillment process that enables retailers to meet demands of online customers. Thing commerce further allows companies to track all orders from the moment they are placed until the time they arrive in the &#39;hands&#39; of the consumer. Each part of inventory is monitored using a robust management system that automatically locates all goods from whichever location they are stored in.</p>\n",
